Datasets i used in the project

1.enron1
-is a csv file that contains 5100 emails-- 71% spam and 21% ham 

2.IIIT-D_SMS_Dataset
-This is collection of 2000 real hindhi sms 
-it is a blanced dataset-50% spam and 50% ham

3.rajnathpatel/multilingual-spam-data
-It is a csv file contains 20,000 messages
-contains hindhi,english,spanish data
-They is not the real , They were machine translated
4.chinese-spam-10000
-https://huggingface.co/datasets/reatiny/chinese-spam-10000
-it contains real chinese language (mandarin)
-it is a balanced data of 10,000 records
